OL,9,G0855 Four in a Bed
OL,10,     FThe competition kicks off at
OL,11,     FGreenways of Malvern in
OL,12,     FWorcestershire, where owner Geri
OL,13,     FAtterbury likes to provide a home
OL,14,     Ffrom home, but a lack of en suite
