OL,5,G1100 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,7,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,8,     Ffor one last time to settle some
OL,9,     Fscores and find out how much
OL,10,     Fthey've been paid. Tensions run
OL,11,     Fhigh before the winner is
OL,12,     Fannounced.
