OL,14,     FSharon and Nev love the beautiful
OL,15,     Fisland of Malta and want to buy a
OL,16,     Fholiday home there for all the
OL,17,     Ffamily to enjoy. With a budget of
OL,18,     F#160,000, can Ben Hillman deliver
OL,19,     Ftheir Maltese dream?
